file.name: another-open-api-v3-spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: another open api v3 spec
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  '/api/words/{wordId}':
    parameters:
      - schema:
          type: integer
        name: wordId
        in: path
        required: true
        description: Id of a word
    get:
      summary: Get User Info by User ID
      tags: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Message Found
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Message'
              examples: {}
        '404':
          description: User Not Found
      operationId: get-word
      description: Retrieve the word.
components:
  schemas:
    Message:
      title: Message
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        message:
          type: string
      required:
        - id
        - message
